{"word":"Centurion","slug":"centurion","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Centurion</b> A commander of one hundred soldiers in the Roman army<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=45'>Mar 15:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=32'>Act 21:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=22&verse=26'>Act 22:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=23&verse=17'>Act 23:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=23&verse=23'>Act 23:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=24&verse=23'>Act 24:23</a><br/> Of Capernaum, comes to Jesus in behalf of his servant<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=13'>Mat 8:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=7&verse=10'>Luk 7:10</a><br/> In charge of the soldiers who crucified Jesus, testifies, &#187;Truly this was the Son of God,&#171;<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=54'>Mat 27:54</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=39'>Mar 15:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=47'>Luk 23:47</a><br/><a href='S:Cornelius'>Cornelius</a>; <a href='S:Julius'>Julius</a>"}]}